Extension oplightbox2 for eZ publish
====================================

Goal:
-----

- Embed lightbox 2 image gallery in eZFlow or eZWebin galleries

"Lightbox is a simple, unobtrusive script used to overlay images on the current page.
It's a snap to setup and works on all modern browsers."
by Lokesh Dhakar

- You can find more informations here: http://www.huddletogether.com/projects/lightbox2/


Requirements:
-------------

- eZ Publish 4.x or later
- eZFlow or eZWebin

Installation and Troubleshooting:
---------------------------------

- Find more information in INSTALL file ate the root of this extension